|---|---|---|
| **DO-330** | Tool Qualification[reference:14] | Emulator and toolchain qualifyable |
| **DO-331** | Model-Based Development[reference:15] | FIS + FSM models are formal and verifiable |
| **DO-332** | Object-Oriented Programming[reference:16] | Ternary logic + FSM — deterministic by design |
| **DO-333** | Formal Methods[reference:17] | FSM + FIS support formal verification[reference:18] |

**ST-T1024 is aligned with all four DO-178C supplements.**

